      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">A smart ham pairing because the slight sweetness and bright acidity handle glaze and salt without making the meal feel heavy. It is also a useful bottle for leftovers.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-wine-600 mt-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Riesling</p>
    </div>
